```json
FRONTEND: {"message":"Failed to fetch the name of the cluster in which the pod is runningmetadata: GCE metadata \"instance/attributes/cluster-name\" not defined","severity":"error","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:13:55.218693039Z"}
